  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "### 1. Verificación de Métrica y Subida/Bajada (Teoría de Tétradas)\n\nDemuestra que el toolkit contrae e hidrata índices arriba/abajo correctamente usando `SmartContract`.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "DefMetric[-1, metric[-a, -b], CDMet, {\";\", \"\\\\nabla\"}];\nDefMetric[-1, eta[-II, -JJ], CDEta, {\"|\", \"D\"}];\nSetDisplayName[eta, \"\\\\[Eta]\"];\nSetTensorFormatting[eta];\nSetTensorFormatting[metric];\nSetDisplayName[metric, \"g\"];\n\nFastTensor[Vb[II, -nu]]; SetDisplayName[Vb, \"e\"];\n\nexpr1 = eta[II, JJ] * Vb[-JJ, mu];\nPrint[\"Output A (Estado Inicial - sin contraer): \"];\nexpr1\nPrint[\"Output B (Estado Final - subida de indice): \"];\nSmartContract[expr1]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-print-output\"><div class=\"wl-print-line\"><span class=\"wl-ps\">** </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrttn5y0-mfwu191\" data-page-width-em=\"62\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtEZWZUZW5zb3J9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">DefTensor</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">: Defining </span><span class=\"wl-ps\">symmetric metric tensor </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrttn5y3-h6kylsj\" data-page-width-em=\"62\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXttZXRyaWN9XGxlZnQoLWEsLWJccmlnaHQp\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">metric</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">. </span><span class=\"wl-ps\"></span></div></div><div class=\"wl-print-output\"><div class=\"wl-print-line\"><span class=\"wl-ps\">** </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrttn602-wwqd639\" data-page-width-em=\"62\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtEZWZUZW5zb3J9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">DefTensor</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">: Defining </span><span class=\"wl-ps\">antisymmetric tensor </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrttn605-1rsldeh\" data-page-width-em=\"62\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtlcHNpbG9ubWV0cmljfVxsZWZ0KC1hLC1iLC1jLC1cbWF0aHJte211fVxyaWdodCk=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">epsilonmetric</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">mu</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">. </span><span class=\"wl-p